snippet.title: Delicious Burger - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2664900/Delicious_Burger/

Delicious Burger is a game which you prepare hamburgers based on customers' desires.

Game Features:
- Enjoy the entertaining burger preparing experience
- Prepare orders with grill, fryer and beverage machine
- Decorate the shop as you wish
- Many customers and orders
- Wide variety of burger toppings
- Unlockable breads, ingredients and drinks
- Unlockable floors, wallpapers, curtains, plants, tables and chairs
